{"tid":818424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收數佬涉禁錮強姦案退庭商議2日無裁決 法官解釋口交不屬性行為","createTime":"2018-09-14T05:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T06:13:05.000Z","uid":75969,"like":28,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"31f8b1f6adccf1f8ddf31e8f826a5a16cdc95a77","tid":818424,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180913/_2018091320543875087.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180913%2F_2018091320543875087.jpg&h=f4f78e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">法官決定讓陪審團先行休息，明早再議。資料圖片<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n欠債女子前年9月因未能償還1.5萬元貸款，被3名「收數佬」禁錮在時鐘酒店，期間更被1名男子強姦。2名涉案男子否認強姦罪及非法禁錮罪受審，6男1女陪審團昨早11時許退庭商議後，直至今晚8時仍未能達致有效裁決。法官決定讓陪審團先行休息，明早再議。<br />\n<br />\n陪審團晚上向法官邱智立提問，口交能否達致法律上的「強姦」，邱官解釋在法律上性行為僅指透過陰莖進入陰道性交，卻不包括口交。<br />\n<br />\n案發於2016年9月13日，被告孫文進及黃振昌被控在旺角砵蘭街華美大廈一間時鐘酒店的房間內，非法禁錮女事主；後者又涉嫌在房間廁所內強姦她。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：黃梓生<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/817018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F817018&d=prQzaSRThAvUF1LR3lMCpJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8c181903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F817018&h=3abe71e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/817018</a><br />\n<br />\n原來口交唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e710c37abfd81e4bf0e177dce75420040caddc","tid":818424,"uid":25858,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:57:28.000Z","msg":"口爆呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec13aad4e239b3c437d32ba0d61dae754d22007f","tid":818424,"uid":108467,"like":137,"dislike":7,"score":130,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T05:58:23.000Z","ms